                        "text": "Why did you go to the X-Men for help?",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/magneto/1_sanctuary1_140_051",
                            "text": "%MAGNETOSIMPLE%: Believe me, it wasn't an easy decision. But after Apocalypse attacked Genosha, I realized my people were more important than my pride.",
