                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: But the X-Men go against everything you believe in.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/magneto/1_sanctuary1_140_053",
                                            "text": "%MAGNETOSIMPLE%: Yes, but they can be trusted once they've given their word - unlike many of my other associates. Still, the X-Men aren't above blackmail.",
